Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.19,0:00:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.79,0:00:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在大家都静静睡下的夜晚\Nみんなが寝静まった夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从窗口眺望夜空的话\N窓から空を見ていると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.69,0:00:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以看到很厉害的东西\Nとっても　すごいものを　見たんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人们都笑者说\N大人は誰も笑いながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我电视看太多了\Nテレビの見過ぎと言うけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我绝对绝对\N僕は　絶対に絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会说谎\N嘘なんか言ってない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.79,0:00:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不会用名为常识的眼镜\N常識と言う眼鏡で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.19,0:00:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我们的世界\N僕たちの世界は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行窥视\Nのぞけやしないのさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘记了梦想的\N夢を忘れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古老的地球人啊\N古い地球人よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇妙的感觉\N不思議な気持ち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.93,0:01:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.71,0:01:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第五話 捷度的決心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.35,0:01:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這難看的MS是你帶來的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.99,0:01:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉阿,幹什麼?有何貴幹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.23,0:01:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蓋蒙大人,我想來幫你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.60,0:02:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用蓋傑號打敗Z高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.49,0:02:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣你們就很容易對付亞加瑪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.64,0:02:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在殖民地是收破爛東西為主\N蓋傑是我做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.32,0:02:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的技巧非常好\N殖民地以收破爛東西為生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.12,0:02:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說亞古捷斯要對付Z高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.68,0:02:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就欣賞你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.20,0:02:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本人生性喜歡幹大事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.96,0:02:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽好,馬士文\N獲得殖民地居民的協助是很重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.99,0:02:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會使我們工作順利\N這點你要謹記在心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.39,0:02:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,這男人是殖民地的居民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.87,0:02:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了,我接受你的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.54,0:02:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下子事情有趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.97,0:02:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信這男人妥當嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.46,0:03:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著,我們有必要\N與殖民星的人成為朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.27,0:03:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是哈曼大人的想法\N又是哈曼大人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.45,0:03:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.96,0:03:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蓋蒙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.96,0:03:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要跟你談談,請跟我到艦橋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.94,0:03:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前,請先聽聽我的條件\N什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.09,0:03:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出擊時,你們的MS必須支援我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.98,0:03:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,支援?可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.82,0:03:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要當候補駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.50,0:03:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉杜艦長很看好你的技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.29,0:03:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你前途有希望阿\N我看過很多人,你資質最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.91,0:03:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要這麼說!亞加瑪當我們基地的話\N我就答應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我也要去\N我贊成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.44,0:03:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也感到有點興趣,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.88,0:03:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪不是遊樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.44,0:03:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼就別再談了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.10,0:04:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥,當駕駛員好過收破爛啊\N這樣我們的生活就有規律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.82,0:04:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪的人也會供你讀書\N吵死了,讀書到學校讀就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.43,0:04:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.82,0:04:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下,捷度!\N我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.58,0:04:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥,你要去哪裏?!\N學校阿,我去讀書阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.63,0:04:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又發脾氣了\N冠武,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.62,0:04:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洗達,冠武,你們會迷路的\N花姊姊,我一定會說服我哥哥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.17,0:04:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請對亞加瑪的人說\N別放棄的太早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.59,0:04:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次真的要出擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.82,0:04:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在那裏幹什麼?\N糟了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.32,0:04:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准動!不然我就開槍\N你開什麼玩笑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.44,0:04:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經等一個小時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.04,0:04:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若說我能派的支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.86,0:04:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有兩架MS\N香格里拉的居民不知會做何感想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.75,0:05:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對亞古捷斯的印象會大壞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.56,0:05:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時就有辱哈曼大人之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.51,0:05:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我所愛的哈曼大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.06,0:05:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是像你求救的可憐小羊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.32,0:05:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請將智慧與勇氣賜給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.35,0:05:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你,哈曼大人\N哈曼大人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.34,0:05:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.99,0:05:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡\N你什麼都沒看到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.38,0:05:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好辛苦,我什麼都沒看到沒聽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.83,0:05:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小羊的話也沒聽到\N什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.17,0:05:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什麼也沒說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.26,0:05:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你聽錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.67,0:06:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,你很懂事作戰結束後\N我給你一個禮拜的有薪假日是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.07,0:06:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.30,0:06:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,你來做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.25,0:06:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,出擊準備作好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.30,0:06:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是這樣?\N是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.19,0:06:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.62,0:06:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蓋蒙,準備出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.94,0:06:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我蓋蒙大人,你是我的部下\N什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.49,0:06:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戈圖,照他的話做\N馬世文大人...我瞭解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.13,0:06:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有兩個部下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.67,0:06:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬世文大將\N我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.05,0:06:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准跑的比隊長快\N想被開除嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.38,0:07:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,港口那艘船有MS出擊了\N這是怎麼一回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.75,0:07:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們想攻擊亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.47,0:07:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花姊姊\N你哥哥在家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.15,0:07:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都去學校了\N他們都突然發神經了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.31,0:07:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,哥哥到殖民地公民學校去了\N說怎樣也不肯當軍人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.99,0:07:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,車子借一下 等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.40,0:07:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小偷阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.19,0:07:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他真的去學校了嗎?\N去看看就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.62,0:07:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海蓮 在 麥克.比魯呢 在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.72,0:07:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莊尼 在 艾瑪 在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.15,0:07:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老師,你沒叫我的名子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.44,0:07:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度.桑達,你來幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.59,0:07:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是每個人\N都得接受義務教育嗎 好痛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.43,0:08:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才一來學校就睡覺\N太看不起人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.45,0:08:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.91,0:08:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼? 不知道\N這樣壓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.36,0:08:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就有白色的粉跑出來\N好好玩,我也想玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.27,0:08:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊有好多,你去拿來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.99,0:08:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.85,0:08:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟過來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.16,0:08:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.65,0:09:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,桑達\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.71,0:09:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你來做這個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.71,0:09:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎?當然\N傷腦筋  快點 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.42,0:09:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.18,0:09:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度他們呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.80,0:09:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在讀書阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.32,0:09:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,發生大事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.85,0:09:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?艾利,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.12,0:09:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪受到三架MS攻擊\N什麼?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.65,0:09:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過不准飛在我前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.18,0:09:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是...什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.44,0:09:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZG...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.09,0:09:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是Z高達,可惡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.63,0:10:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蓋蒙...大人,你幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.33,0:10:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒看到那個字嗎!\N那是Z高達的挑戰書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.99,0:10:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挑戰書?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.24,0:10:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾利,誰說是攻擊亞加瑪\N敵人跑到學校來才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.54,0:10:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是收破爛的蓋蒙大人\NZ高達,來與我蓋蒙大人決鬥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.10,0:10:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然我就破壞學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.50,0:10:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怕了嗎?Z高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.44,0:10:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快滾出來吧\N不然我殺光學校的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.52,0:11:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你在附近\N你不出來我就真的破壞學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.75,0:11:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不說謊是我的優點,Z高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.64,0:11:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫他閉嘴吧,我聽的都頭痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.14,0:11:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,是花,花回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.29,0:11:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家不能怕,不然真的會被壓死\N大家來幫我忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.11,0:11:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼幫你忙...?\N不要阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.91,0:11:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好怕阿\N媽媽叫我們不可以冒險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.84,0:11:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度 怎麼辦?要逃嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.53,0:11:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒那個空了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.64,0:11:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不出來我就殺光學生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.69,0:11:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來我們的任務\N不是攻擊亞加瑪阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.96,0:11:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查他們不知干的怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.93,0:11:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 來吧 開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.45,0:12:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 你以為你這樣很有型嗎\N向薩克看齊一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.11,0:12:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是只有薩克才是MS阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.46,0:12:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的蓋傑的性能\N比戰鬥用MS的機動性好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.37,0:12:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我開發的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.83,0:12:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這短腿的哪有機動力啊\N不要臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.26,0:12:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鬼!\N敢看不起我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.06,0:12:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,短腳蓋蒙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.06,0:12:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鬼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.21,0:12:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧,艾莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.07,0:12:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.48,0:12:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Yeah~~!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.98,0:12:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹的好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鬼...!不可原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.99,0:13:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要挽回顏面\N起來吧,蓋傑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.39,0:13:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敢看輕我蓋傑的人都該死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.70,0:13:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算找爸媽來道歉也沒用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.66,0:13:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.39,0:13:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,門口被弄壞了\N不可以這樣做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.14,0:13:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可看低人阿!\NZ高達不出來,你們就是人質了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.34,0:13:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達發動準備完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.22,0:13:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出動時請把頭壓低\N瞭解!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.46,0:13:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花,去與捷度會合\N想辦法讓他駕駛Z高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.93,0:13:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能的話我希望不必麻煩到他\N說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.43,0:13:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達,出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.63,0:14:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.25,0:14:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達! Z高達! Z高達!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.67,0:14:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能叫他就會出現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.98,0:14:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們的心情我瞭解\N可是叫是沒有用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.41,0:14:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了!Z高達來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.28,0:14:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於來了\NZ高達,真是大牌阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.41,0:14:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏交給他吧\N我們加入混戰傷到居民有不好的影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.96,0:14:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.71,0:14:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達,你要去哪裏?\N我有人質阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.11,0:14:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的想打倒Z高達的話\N就到適合決鬥的地方來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.35,0:14:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想要叫我走嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.51,0:15:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的善良,害怕會牽連到小孩\N你是住在這裏的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.31,0:15:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將小孩當做人質有什麼用啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.78,0:15:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著,在這裏使用雷射炮\N會毀滅這個殖民地的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.16,0:15:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,這裏是殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.35,0:15:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蓋蒙!你太卑鄙了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艙門關不起來?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.03,0:15:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達,你虛有其名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.60,0:15:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點程度是毀不了Z高達的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.43,0:15:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挺有一手的\N機艙會移動?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.20,0:15:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛員是女人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.50,0:15:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個駕駛員真大膽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.87,0:15:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瓦斯槽?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.75,0:16:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度! 比查,把那些瓦斯槽弄掉\N來幫忙吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.93,0:16:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人,乖乖認輸吧\N不可能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.37,0:16:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的!\N是河流...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.96,0:16:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.53,0:16:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣沒問題嗎?\N這樣做,應該沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.82,0:16:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,這邊隨時可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.10,0:16:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你快乖乖聽話當成我的東西吧,Z高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.29,0:16:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是怕力量太大會傷到殖民地\N你還不知道嗎!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.30,0:16:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎!是嗎!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.70,0:16:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行了...怎麼會這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.76,0:17:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贏了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.77,0:17:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破MS阿,打贏了壞掉的Z高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.00,0:17:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼好高興的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.14,0:17:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.69,0:17:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以了,比查,方向正確\N好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.69,0:17:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼跟著我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.29,0:17:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.96,0:17:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.72,0:17:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.02,0:17:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是機會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.55,0:17:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是瓦斯槽\N那麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.43,0:18:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣?破瓦斯槽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個小鬼!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.15,0:18:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是花小姐嗎?你沒事吧\恩,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.76,0:18:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.76,0:18:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他又來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.02,0:18:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.89,0:18:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個平民竟敢小看Z高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.38,0:18:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.64,0:18:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要把你和那個臭小子一起打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.08,0:18:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花小姐,我在這裏阿!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.68,0:18:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!\N花小姐你清醒點吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.83,0:18:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.50,0:19:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花小姐趁現在下去,快!\N我還要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.97,0:19:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要一直當我的椅子嗎\N不要阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.94,0:19:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,Z高達的力量足以毀滅殖民地阿\N知道了 糟了,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.28,0:19:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該用溫柔點的方式讓我下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.74,0:19:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別囉唆,快離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.84,0:19:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好..!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.00,0:19:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快\N知道移動式駕駛艙的威力了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.83,0:19:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰怕你阿\N這次換我攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.26,0:19:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣?認輸了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.22,0:20:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的眼睛再打轉阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.97,0:20:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這裏!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.53,0:20:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停不下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.97,0:20:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是自作自受\N暫時這樣反省吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.36,0:20:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託,讓我停下來\N我只是受命行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.24,0:20:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要找藉口了\N真的,就是停在港口的安多拉號的將軍拜託我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.94,0:20:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安多拉?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.39,0:20:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得救了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.17,0:20:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些傢伙是不是\N胸口有一朵紅玫瑰的臭男人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.66,0:20:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的,你怎麼會知道?\N他是亞古捷斯的馬士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.38,0:20:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被他強迫來作戰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.72,0:20:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請原諒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.15,0:21:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來又是他\N那個叫馬士文的真是不可原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.78,0:21:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託那個收破爛的果然是錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.63,0:21:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然這樣\N就直接開安多啦攻擊亞加瑪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.76,0:21:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但這樣會使居民受害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.87,0:21:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒參加這次作戰的用心\N不就白費了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.31,0:21:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的對\N我怎麼忘記這麼重要的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.68,0:21:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我太累了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.37,0:21:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,疲倦會使人犯下錯誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.43,0:21:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,操之過急會使人民成為敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.20,0:21:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要多加注意,馬士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.85,0:21:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人說的對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.19,0:21:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就等到實驗MS組合成吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.44,0:21:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本艦還有幾個需要測試的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.19,0:21:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.50,0:21:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是哈瑪 哈瑪 嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.96,0:21:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼大人,請賜給我力量吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.60,0:21:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次敵人何時會來不知道\NZ高達借給我好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.87,0:22:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以大家一起來亞加瑪不是很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.72,0:22:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這我早拒絕過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.71,0:22:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是,捷度哥哥\NZ高達要停在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.27,0:22:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對喔,我沒地方停MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.41,0:22:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼大不好藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.42,0:22:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,維修費也很貴\N對阿,亞加瑪會免費維修的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.46,0:22:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法,那就交給亞加瑪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.94,0:22:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼,請注意別破壞環境,好好運回去吧\N我也這麼打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.10,0:22:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在没有道路的荒野里\N道もない荒れた原野に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.10,0:22:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建造铁路真是一件辛苦差事\Nレールを作るのは苦しいことさ
